high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the butter knife up from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the counter with a coffee maker on it.
Slice the apple in the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Go left and turn to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and then remove it after cooking.
Cross the room and turn to the right to face the small black table.
Put the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of apple on a table.

high_descs: Cross the room to stand at the counter between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn and carry the knife to the counter with the coffee maker, which is by the table.
Slice the apple that's in the green trash bin below the counter using the knife.
Place the knife in the trash bin with the apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the trash bin.
Turn and carry the apple slice to the stove.
Open the microwave above the stove, place the apple inside, and then remove it once heated.
Turn and carry the apple slice to the small black table in the corner, which is next to a large white table.
Place the apple slice on the right side of the loaf of bread on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of apple on the black table in the corner.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk all the way to the counter that's to the left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk until you're even with the coffee maker to your left and then turn left and walk to it.
Cut up the apple that's in the garbage.
Put the knife in the garbage.
Pick up a chunk of apple.
Go back to where you got the butter knife and take a large step right so you are standing in front of the stove and more importantly the microwave.
Warm the chunk of apple in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and turn right and walk to the small black table.
Put the chunk of apple in the corner to the right of the bread near you.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm chunk of apple on the table.
